#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/dev/skills/design-and-build/vercel-composition-patterns/rules/architecture-avoid-boolean-props.md savings=-12%
M||tx|---
M||titl|Avoid Boolean Prop Proliferation
M||impa|ct
M||impa|prevents unmaintainable cp variants
M||tags|composition, props, architecture
M||tx|---
M|Avoi|tx|Don't add boolean props like `isThread`, `isEditing`, `isDMThread` to customize
M|Avoi|tx|cp behavior. Each boolean doubles possible states and creates
M|Avoi|tx|unmaintainable conditional logic. Use composition instead.
M|Avoi|**In|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|fn Composer({
M|Avoi|tx|onSubmit,
M|Avoi|tx|isThread,
M|Avoi|tx|channelId,
M|Avoi|tx|isDMThread,
M|Avoi|tx|dmId,
M|Avoi|tx|isEditing,
M|Avoi|tx|isForwarding,
M|Avoi|}|Props) {
M|Avoi|tx|return (
M|Avoi|tx|<form>
M|Avoi|tx|<Header />
M|Avoi|tx|<Input />
M|Avoi|tx|{isDMThread ? (
M|Avoi|tx|<AlsoSendToDMField id={dmId} />
M|Avoi|)|isThread ? (
M|Avoi|tx|<AlsoSendToChannelField id={channelId} />
M|Avoi|)|null}
M|Avoi|tx|{isEditing ? (
M|Avoi|tx|<EditActions />
M|Avoi|)|isForwarding ? (
M|Avoi|tx|<ForwardActions />
M|Avoi|)|(
M|Avoi|tx|<DefaultActions />
M|Avoi|tx|)}
M|Avoi|tx|<Footer onSubmit={onSubmit} />
M|Avoi|tx|</form>
M|Avoi|tx|)
M|Avoi|tx|}
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|**Co|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|// Channel composer
M|Avoi|tx|fn ChannelComposer() {
M|Avoi|tx|return (
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Frame>
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Header />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Input />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Footer>
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Attachments />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Formatting />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Emojis />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Submit />
M|Avoi|tx|</Composer.Footer>
M|Avoi|tx|</Composer.Frame>
M|Avoi|tx|)
M|Avoi|tx|}
M|Avoi|tx|// Thread composer - adds "also send to channel" field
M|Avoi|func|{ channelId: string }) {
M|Avoi|tx|return (
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Frame>
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Header />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Input />
M|Avoi|tx|<AlsoSendToChannelField id={channelId} />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Footer>
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Formatting />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Emojis />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Submit />
M|Avoi|tx|</Composer.Footer>
M|Avoi|tx|</Composer.Frame>
M|Avoi|tx|)
M|Avoi|tx|}
M|Avoi|tx|// Edit composer - different footer actions
M|Avoi|tx|fn EditComposer() {
M|Avoi|tx|return (
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Frame>
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Input />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Footer>
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Formatting />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.Emojis />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.CancelEdit />
M|Avoi|tx|<Composer.SaveEdit />
M|Avoi|tx|</Composer.Footer>
M|Avoi|tx|</Composer.Frame>
M|Avoi|tx|)
M|Avoi|tx|}
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|tx|Each variant is explicit abt what it renders. We can share internals w/o
M|Avoi|tx|sharing a single monolithic parent.